com.plugins.plugin

Interface Plugin

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JarPluginBase, PluginList

    public interface Plugin

    interface marker for a java class as a plugin

    interface used to mark a java class as a plugin clients of this interface must provide the interface name of used as plugin in a meta data string called interface the interface property must be the fully interface name with the package name for example java.lang.Object
